Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著嘛接著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是有人想要您的命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有刺客進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來...人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片名：影子Shadow（1）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一、黑暗的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！大人被殺了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...華龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵大人 從剛才一直等到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死目標的人並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕也是忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孫六那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是不相信我們 又去找了別的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到後面去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種工作要何時才結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有不滿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們忍著想在 漫長的太平時代活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沒有別的選擇餘地的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 時代很快就要變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沾在我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶青菜來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以拜託你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的對象是大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不容易哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是...你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對女忍者熟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女忍者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的忍者不是落魄到 做保鏢就是當殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作給她來做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的能力很優秀 你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人畏懼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！又來了！可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！這隻小偷狸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是客人要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我絕不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 可惡 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小乙 把那只臭狸交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風是鼯鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什麼都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之把它...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩貴！對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的給我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孫六啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子又要忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這件事跟小孩無關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孫六大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒做嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您與葵大人的事情談完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才能跟你...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會兒讓你更舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是 有沒有什麼特殊的事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵那女人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天講話 話種有話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼特殊的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華龍大人也來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不行 剛才你偷吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 華龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說昨夜有人 妨礙您的工作 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是彩貴說的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小乙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡等我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的叫阿龍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幕府真是落魄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天派不同的女人 來服侍我這個外姓諸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓小的來為您洗背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想來拿下我的人頭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現在殺死我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反對幕府政策的人將會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可怕的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的只是 奉命來服侍大人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞這種小把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惹人憐惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡只有您與我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣勾引我 是逃不了我的責罰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人！大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人 請趕快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慘了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到最後時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血？血？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血！血！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.67,0:24:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的侍者們怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.14,0:24:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客已經殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你殺死的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.16,0:24:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你獎賞的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你的身手來看 你是忍著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是皇室派來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只身手不凡 身材也是好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.30,0:25:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？要不要為我工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會虧待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後像你這樣的忍著 會越來越需要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大人